{
  "stem": "8947.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he was riding and over them and killing them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You know, and was ride-- you know when you want to-- you see in the movies that thing, when you-- you just love to go and-- and crush people, you know?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I never forget-- I have this narrative in my book-- the aftermath.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I was praying to God, if you have my book, you are going to find this-- this-- this narrative, in which, you know, on-- I was praying to God to help us.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You know, I mean, I was-- I can't tell you what I felt.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I felt such a rage and such a helplessness.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And-- and I was just hoping that somehow, one day, I will go away from here, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I can tell you many stories.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But this is-- this is something that I still see those bodies on the ground and this-- this-- this driver, like a mad devil, you know, riding over their bodies.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I can never forget that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Now, I have seen many horrible things in Auschwitz besides this, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "You see what happened to the other side, the people who were taken to the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Probably you know the story that they were given towels and-- and-- see, there-- there were four crematory units in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And each was consisting of under one [INAUDIBLE] viaduct and the gas chambers in the crematory ovens, you know?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And as I told you, the gas-- the gas chamber had a-- was written bath house.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And it has also a peephole.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It was administered gas by Sonderkommando, SS Sonderkommando.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "From-- from-- from above, you know, there was an opening through which gas was administered-- Zyklon B, mixed with cyanide.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And then also, there were ducts from outside.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "You know, they were special.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
